<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>OTP Verification | mern-setup-system</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #0a0a0c;
        font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #e0e0e0;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background-color: #121214;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid #2d2d30;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
      }

      /* Header */
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #06b6d4 100%);
        padding: 40px 24px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .header-subtitle {
        font-size: 13px;
        opacity: 0.9;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      /* Content */
      .content {
        padding: 40px;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 15px;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
        color: #b0b0b0;
      }

      /* OTP Box */
      .otp-box {
        background-color: #1c1c1f;
        border: 1px solid #3f3f46;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 32px;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 30px 0;
      }

      .otp-label {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #a1a1aa;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }

      .otp-code {
        font-size: 48px;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 8px;
        color: #06b6d4;
        font-family: 'Monaco', 'Courier New', monospace;
        margin: 15px 0;
        text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.2);
      }

      .otp-expiry {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #71717a;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }

      /* Action Button */
      .button-wrapper {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 35px 0;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #4f46e5;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        padding: 16px 40px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 700;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      /* Security Notice */
      .security-note {
        background-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
        border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
        padding: 16px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #f87171;
        margin: 25px 0;
      }

      /* Footer */
      .footer {
        background-color: #0a0a0c;
        border-top: 1px solid #2d2d30;
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
      }

      .footer a {
        color: #06b6d4;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .dev-credit {
        margin-top: 10px;
        color: #4f46e5;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
        .otp-code { font-size: 38px; letter-spacing: 6px; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">CODE BIRUNI</div>
        <div class="header-subtitle">mern-setup-system v{{version}}</div>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h2>Verify Your Account</h2>

        <p>
          Hello {{userName}},<br><br>
          To complete your registration on our platform and finalize the account setup, please use the following one-time password (OTP).
        </p>

        <div class="otp-box">
          <div class="otp-label">Verification Code</div>
          <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
          <div class="otp-expiry">
            ⏱ Valid for 10 minutes only
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="security-note">
          <strong>Security Warning:</strong> 
          Do not share this code with anyone. Our support team will never ask for your verification code.
        </div>

        <div class="button-wrapper">
          <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="button">
            Go to Verification Page
          </a>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 13px; text-align: center;">
          If you did not initiate this request, please contact our support immediately or ignore this email.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>© {{currentYear}} <strong>Code Biruni</strong>. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated security message from <strong>mern-setup-system</strong>.</p>
        <div class="dev-credit">Architected by Robius Sani</div>
        <p style="margin-top: 15px;">
          Support: <a href="mailto:hafazrobiussani@gmail.com">hafazrobiussani@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>